{"id": 2839, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你发现哪些正常的情绪表达已经变得羞于启齿了？", "description": "来说说你都咋样用力过猛地扮演一名情绪稳定的成年人的。（题图来自：iStock©️roberuto ）", "record_count": 5024, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190312100731T8rmBsEWRegOY5i3.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-19T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 334080, "content": "除了某些大事，其他事引起的任何情绪都不敢发朋友圈了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498209}, {"id": 334081, "content": "朋友圈不可以抱怨那里那里受伤了那里那里不开心，因为父母会看到他们会担心。只能在QQ上和沙雕网友隔着不知道多远的网站互相安慰。", "image": "img/option/option/20190320083007hJmTpBblv3wV1AsG", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476013}, {"id": 334082, "content": "你的开心，你的苦恼，你的奇葩想法，都设为啦仅自己可见。或者……“有点文化”地发条动态。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407519}, {"id": 334083, "content": "不敢发朋友圈，怕别人认为我在炫耀:)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507086}, {"id": 340227, "content": "发心情的地方从qq空间到朋友圈到微博，最后到各种小众app", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641556}, {"id": 334084, "content": "想拒绝别人的要求但是怎么都开不了口", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613757}, {"id": 334085, "content": "想喜欢的人知道自己的心意 又不想被他知道\n内心十分矛盾\n就如：发特别的朋友圈只限于给喜欢的人看 但总时不时私密而后又开放\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613762}, {"id": 334342, "content": "从不敢在别人面前吐露真心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 335878, "content": "心情不好，不爱发一大串文字，分享一首歌代表自己的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620535}, {"id": 334087, "content": "生气也不敢了呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582069}, {"id": 334088, "content": "自己不开心不能说出来，因为除了我没有人不开心。那我把不开心说出来就没有意义了，别人只会觉得我做作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543301}, {"id": 335112, "content": "定时定期删朋友圈\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616465}, {"id": 334090, "content": "面对生活有着美好的憧憬但自己的却迷茫的活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572249}, {"id": 334091, "content": "一有理想就被说好高骛远", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460529}, {"id": 334861, "content": "当我说享受寂寞的时候他们都说我骚", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298793}, {"id": 334350, "content": "明明觉得很无聊，但还要哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378846}, {"id": 335632, "content": "想与人分享生活，却怕被说太吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619106}, {"id": 334097, "content": "想表达自己任何真正的想法时，却发现还不如不说", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590346}, {"id": 334098, "content": "从来不相信任何一个人\n对于陌生人和气 对家人暴躁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583836}, {"id": 334099, "content": "朋友圈空间的动态一直都很羞于启齿，让我更难过的是，我连悲伤的情绪都不知道如何向外界表达了，除了我的密友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1597403}, {"id": 334100, "content": "不敢随便在朋友圈崩溃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611880}, {"id": 334101, "content": "不敢回答开放性的问题怕被觉得幼稚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611880}, {"id": 334102, "content": "发泄不满和记录生活好像已经不存在朋友圈了，我的朋友圈明明是我自己来管理，为什么别人还要BB", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613844}, {"id": 334103, "content": "除了开心以外所有的情绪表达之前都要反思自己这么做是不是不应该", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120961}, {"id": 334104, "content": "不觉得羞于启齿，只是感到绝望，很多意愿就算表达出来也改变不了对方固执己见。我可能不是一个合格的成年人，我只能保持沉默随波逐流。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613859}, {"id": 334105, "content": "拒绝不喜欢的人（事）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601610}, {"id": 334106, "content": "一方面觉得空间或微信只是记录自己生活的，但是又真的很在意点赞量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613012}, {"id": 333851, "content": "爱国💔", "image": null, "praise_count": 230, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216372}, {"id": 334107, "content": "不喜欢政府的某些行为", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516920}, {"id": 333852, "content": "流眼泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433133}, {"id": 334109, "content": "可以帮我递只笔吗？✏️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613872}, {"id": 333854, "content": "发朋友圈要深思熟虑够不够深度", "image": null, "praise_count": 249, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612994}, {"id": 333855, "content": "心情不好时候不敢跟人诉说，只频繁换头像。", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563528}, {"id": 334879, "content": "我喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480187}, {"id": 333856, "content": "不同的朋友圈内容会屏蔽不同的人群", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483055}, {"id": 334112, "content": "抱怨自己活得不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613880}, {"id": 333857, "content": "发朋友圈要开始考虑影响了…但发朋友圈的原因本来不是记录自己的生活吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 616, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467614}, {"id": 334113, "content": "朋友圈里寂静的像个死人，微博里活跃的像个疯子，只敢把心里的想法说给陌生人，这大概是我最大的悲哀", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613740}, {"id": 333858, "content": "越长大越不能对朋友说你的某些不快乐，越不能说我在乎你。显得矫情幼稚。可能是朋友之间的关系越来越淡，越来越复杂了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324280}, {"id": 334114, "content": "觉得一些人很恶心，却还要如无其事的相处。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553350}, {"id": 333859, "content": "发朋友圈全部设置私密可见", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1597979}, {"id": 333860, "content": "外人看来分外靠谱，家人眼中千疮百孔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118083}, {"id": 334116, "content": "我就是不能好好说话了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1589170}, {"id": 334372, "content": "和朋友聊天常常尴尬，因为不懂那些他们一天一换的梗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614378}, {"id": 335140, "content": "没有办法表达真实。只能包裹一层娱乐外壳。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962650}, {"id": 337188, "content": "一切不流于表面的思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 333861, "content": "点一盏明灯，燃希望之火，照亮黑暗的每一个角落", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572250}, {"id": 333862, "content": "不敢哭，只能硬撑在笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1149728}, {"id": 334374, "content": "自我感悟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614384}, {"id": 333863, "content": "累", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}]}